data.description: An impressive 374’ paved driveway leads to the front door of this immense custom home designed w/many features nestled on a private 5 acre fenced lot. Bamboo hardwood floors bring warmth & extravagance to the main & lower level living areas. The open floor plan includes an inviting gourmet kitchen complete with maple cabinets, a spacious walk-in pantry, granite countertops, & top of the line appliances including a Samsung gas cooktop and hood, Sharp built-in microwave drawer, & Bosch gas double oven & dishwasher. Entertaining is a delight with the 9’ custom island including an endcap of butcher’s block for all your baking needs. The spacious living room boasts amazing views of majestic Pikes Peak & the Front Range from the picture windows as well as relaxing enjoyment in front of the gas fireplace. Adjacent to the kitchen is a bonus nook with granite countertops & plenty of storage cabinets that can be used as any type of creative space from a second office to a homework station. The primary bedroom retreat offers substantial space for a sitting area to take in the panoramic views from the bay window as well as a King size bedroom set with plenty of room left over. The ensuite bath invites you to relax after a long day with a luxurious, oversized walk-in shower with custom sitting bench & a triple head shower system, dual sinks, makeup vanity, & plenty of storage space for linens. Just beyond the ensuite are impressive his/her walk-in closets. The main level also includes two additional bedrooms, an office, a full bathroom, & laundry room. The finished basement opens to a home theater/rec room, dry bar, private workout/flex space, & a hobbyist dream room. A third 3/4 bath & substantial 4th bedroom complement the basement. This home is finished w/recessed lighting, spray foam wall insulation, solid core Alder wood doors/trim on the main & lower levels & numerous smart home amenities. Oversized 3 car garage will accommodate full size truck(s), ATV''s and/or workbench.
